request.description:
Get all product variants with discounted prices.

Query Parameters:
- category_id: Filter by category ID (exact match)
- category_name: Filter by category name (case-insensitive partial match)
- min_price: Minimum discounted price
- max_price: Maximum discounted price
- ordering: Order by fields (price, -price, discounted_price, -discounted_price, created_at, -created_at)

Examples:
- /variants/discounts/?category_id=5
- /variants/discounts/?category_name=grocery
- /variants/discounts/?min_price=100&max_price=500
- /variants/discounts/?category_id=5&ordering=-discounted_price
